videos.description: Isaac Likekele throws a back door pass to Cameron McGriff who flushes the one-handed dunk giving the Cowboys their first points of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McGriff puts Oklahoma State on the board with big dunk) 2020/01/06

videos.headline: McGriff puts Oklahoma State on the board with big dunk

videos.description: Jermaine Haley throws the lob to Oscar Tshiebwe for the monster two-handed dunk.
